===Pokémon Trading Card Game===
====Nemona====
Nemona has had one series of unique merchandise released exclusively for the Pokémon Trading Card Game, simply known as '''Nemona''', drawn by [[kirisAki]]. It was released on December 1st, 2023, tying in with the release of [[Shiny Treasure ex]].<ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tJyXvMEKnJQ 【発売前に開封】「シャイニートレジャーex」と同時発売のポケカ新グッズを実物レビュー！新たなフルサイズプレイマットも登場！【ポケモンカード】]- Pokémon Card Channel, ''YouTube''</ref>

